      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Drain the <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then cut the <strong>tofu</strong> into strips</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>",
