      "instruction": "<p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>tofu strips </strong>and <strong>garam masala </strong>to the pan and cook for 6-7 min, turning occasionally until golden and crisp</p><p>Meanwhile, heat a separate, large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
